# NoteFlow core

- Single chronological stream ("The Universal Flow"); no folder hierarchy.
- Three entry types only: `note`, `task`, `link`.
- Filters (ALL/NOTES/TASKS/LINKS) are views over one store, not separate data silos.
- v1: client-side `localStorage` only — no backend unless explicitly requested.
- UI: monochrome, 1px black borders, no border-radius, uppercase section labels.
- Read `docs/idea.md` before adding features outside v1 scope.
